             was indicted for <rs id="t18280529-4-off13" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18280529-4-off13" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280529-4-off13" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               breaking and entering the dwelling-house of 
                     <persName id="t18280529-4-victim112" type="victimName">
                        Septimus 
